'''马德琳·亚娜·科贝尔·奥尔布赖特'''（{{lang-en|Madeleine Jana Korbel Albright}}<ref>{{cite news|last=Sciolino|first=Elaine|title=WOMAN IN THE NEWS; Dukakis's Foreign Policy Adviser: Madeleine Jana Korbel Albright|url=http://www.nytimes.com/1988/07/26/us/woman-dukakis-s-foreign-policy-adviser-madeleine-jana-korbel-albright.html|publisher=New York Times|accessdate=2015-07-19|date=1988-07-26|archive-date=2020-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200901174258/https://www.nytimes.com/1988/07/26/us/woman-dukakis-s-foreign-policy-adviser-madeleine-jana-korbel-albright.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>；{{bd|1937年|5月15日|2022年|3月23日|catIdx=Albright, Madeleine}}<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2013/05/27/us/madeleine-albright-fast-facts |title=Madeleine Albright Fast Facts |publisher=[[CNN|CNN]] |date=2014-05-08 |accessdate=2014-12-31 |archive-date=2020-09-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200930232057/https://www.cnn.com/2013/05/27/us/madeleine-albright-fast-facts |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.newrepublic.com/article/books-and-arts/90326/memory-goes-war |title=Memory Goes to War |author=Roger Cohen |work=The New Republic |accessdate=2014-12-31 |archive-date=2015-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150913105122/http://www.newrepublic.com/article/books-and-arts/90326/memory-goes-war |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=来自马德琳家人的声明（推特）|url=https://twitter.com/madeleine/status/1506699712199593985|access-date=2022-03-23|work=Twitter|language=英语|archive-date=2022-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220331010544/https://twitter.com/madeleine/status/1506699712199593985|dead-url=no}}</ref>）原名'''玛丽·亚娜·科贝洛娃'''（{{lang-cs|Marie Jana Korbelová}}），是一位出生于[[捷克斯洛伐克|捷克斯洛伐克]]的[[美国|美国]]政治人物和外交官，美国第64任[[美国国务卿|国务卿]]，也是美國首位女性國務卿，现为奥尔布赖特石桥集团主席和[[乔治敦大学|乔治敦大学]][[埃德蒙·A·沃尔什外交学院|埃德蒙·A·沃尔什外交学院]]教授。她拥有[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]博士学位和许多荣誉学位。2012年5月，她获得时任[[美国总统|美国总统]][[贝拉克·奥巴马|贝拉克·奥巴马]]颁发的[[总统自由勋章|总统自由勋章]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://articles.cnn.com/2012-05-29/us/us_medal-of-freedom_1_presidential-medal-highest-civilian-honor-president-barack-obama |publisher=CNN |title=Albright, Dylan among recipients of Presidential Medal of Freedom |date=2012-05-29 |first=Tom |last=Cohen |access-date=2016-07-10 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20140121023440/http://www.cnn.com/2012/05/29/us/medal-of-freedom/index.html |archive-date=2014-01-21 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。她还担任过[[美国外交关系协会|美国外交关系协会]]的董事<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.cfr.org/about/people/board_of_directors.html |title = Board of Directors – Council on Foreign Relations |publisher = Council on Foreign Relations |date = 2006-05-14 |accessdate = 2009-06-01 |archiveurl = https://www.webcitation.org/5tyKXfrAg?url=http://www.cfr.org/about/people/board_of_directors.html |archivedate = 2010-11-03 |deadurl = yes }}</ref>。國務卿任內曾訪問[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国|北朝鮮]]，當時創下到訪[[朝鲜民主主义人民共和国|北朝鮮]]的美國最高級别官員紀錄<ref>{{cite web
|url=http://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/kim/interviews/albright.html
|title=Frontline: Kim's Nuclear Gamble: Interviews: Madeleine Albright
|publisher=PBS
|date=2003-03-27
|accessdate=2009-06-01
|archive-date=2021-04-22
|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210422142141/https://www.pbs.org/wgbh/pages/frontline/shows/kim/interviews/albright.html
|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。除了通晓[[英语|英语]]、[[法语|法语]]、[[俄语|俄语]]和[[捷克语|捷克语]]外，还能说[[波兰语|波兰语]]和[[塞尔维亚-克罗地亚语|塞尔维亚-克罗地亚语]]。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2003/oct/30/usa.emmabrockes | location=London | work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]] | first=Emma | last=Brockes | title=Interview: Madeleine Albright | date=2003-10-30 | accessdate=2016-07-10 | archive-date=2012-11-14 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114162848/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2003/oct/30/usa.emmabrockes | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==生平==
[[File:Houghton_house_Netanyahu_Albright_Arafat.jpg|thumb]][[本雅明·内塔尼亚胡|本雅明·内塔尼亚胡]]（左）和[[巴勒斯坦民族权力机构主席|巴勒斯坦民族权力机构主席]][[亚西尔·阿拉法特|亚西尔·阿拉法特]]（右）会面]] 
歐布萊特出生于[[捷克斯洛伐克共和国|捷克斯洛伐克共和国]][[布拉格|布拉格]]<ref name="birth">{{cite news |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/politics/govt/admin/albright.htm |title=Biography at The Washington Post |publisher=''The Washington Post'' |date=1999-12-15 |accessdate=2009-06-22 |archive-date=2021-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124074303/https://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/politics/govt/admin/albright.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。其父是外交官约瑟夫·科贝尔<ref name="Tablet">{{cite web|url=http://tabletmag.com/podcasts/97886/madeleine-albrights-war-years|title=Madeleine Albright’s War Years|publisher=Tablet Magazine|date=2012-04-26|accessdate=2014-12-31|archive-date=2013-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130310182057/https://www.tabletmag.com/podcasts/97886/madeleine-albrights-war-years|dead-url=no}}</ref>，曾任[[捷克斯洛伐克|捷克斯洛伐克]]駐[[南斯拉夫社会主义联邦共和国|南斯拉夫]]大使。在1948年[[捷克共產黨|捷克共產黨]]上台時，由於反對[[共產主義|共產主義]]，被迫辭職，从[[捷克斯洛伐克|捷克斯洛伐克]]流亡至美国<ref>{{cite web|url=http://libertyellisfoundation.org/passenger-details/czoxMzoiOTAxMTg2NjE2MTgwOSI7/czo5OiJwYXNzZW5nZXIiOw==|title=Passenger Manifest|work=The Statue of Liberty - Ellis Island Foundation|accessdate=2014-12-31}}{{Dead link}}</ref><ref name="Dobbs">{{cite book |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dhZghL4Rr-EC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_ge_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false |title=Madeleine Albright: A twentieth-century odyssey |first=Michael |last=Dobbs |publisher=Henry Holt and Company |accessdate=2014-12-31 |isbn=0-8050-5659-9 |year=1999 |archive-date=2020-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815115636/https://books.google.com/books?id=dhZghL4Rr-EC&printsec=frontcover&source=gbs_ge_summary_r&cad=0#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>。後來創辦了[[丹佛大学|丹佛大学]][[国际研究學院|国际研究學院]]。科贝尔教授是前[[美國国务卿|美國国务卿]][[康多莉扎·赖斯|康多莉扎·赖斯]]在[[丹佛大學|丹佛大學]]時的啟蒙老师。<ref name=autogenerated2>{{cite news|first = Michael|last = Dobbs|title = Josef Korbel's Enduring Foreign Policy Legacy|url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-552426.html|work = The Washington Post|page = A05|date = 2000-12-28|accessdate = 2009-04-09|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121105120122/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1P2-552426.html|archive-date = 2012-11-05|dead-url = yes}}</ref>

歐布萊特是於1957年獲得美國公民資格<ref>Albright, 2003, pp. 34–35.</ref>，並在[[麻省|麻省]][[威爾斯利學院|威爾斯利學院]]修習政治学，1959年毕业。同年她與報業大亨{{le|約瑟·奥尔布赖特|Joseph Medill Patterson Albright}}結婚<ref>Albright, 2003, p. 36.</ref><ref name=autogenerated3>Albright, 2003, p. 47.</ref>，育有三個女兒<ref name=autogenerated5>Albright, 2003, p. 52.</ref>。自此改姓為歐布萊特。1967年重返校園，在[[哥伦比亚大学|哥伦比亚大学]]获得哲学博士学位<ref>Albright, 2003, p. 71.</ref>。其後曾任乔治敦大学国际事务学教授，是该校国家政策中心主任，专门研究美国与[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]、[[东欧|东欧]]国家之关系。

1976年进入政界，任[[吉米·卡特|吉米·卡特]]总统的[[美国国家安全委员会|国家安全委员会]]委员，负责与国会联络<ref name=scott99>{{cite news| first = A.O.| last = Scott| title = Madeleine Albright: The Diplomat Who Mistook Her Life for Statecraft| url = http://www.slate.com/id/25857/| publisher = ''Slate''| date = 1999-04-25| accessdate = 2009-04-09| archive-date = 2011-09-07| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110907232646/http://www.slate.com/id/25857| dead-url = no}}</ref>。1981年[[里根|里根]]担任总统后，奧爾布賴特重返学术界，著有《波兰：政治变化中新闻界的作用》。1983年回到乔治敦大学任教，教授外交。1989年出任[[美國民主党|美國民主党]]全国政策中心主席。

1993年1月[[比尔·克林顿|比尔·克林顿]]上台，委任奧爾布賴特為[[美国常驻联合国代表|美国常驻联合国代表]]<ref>Albright, 2003, p. 131.</ref>。在任期間最為受爭議的事件，莫過於1994年爆发的[[卢旺达大屠杀|卢旺达大屠杀]]事件，奧爾布賴特堅持著不干涉立場，甚至出面阻挠[[联合国|联合国]]干涉盧旺達內政，結果奧爾布賴特與聯合國秘書長關係曾一度極為緊張<ref name=ms207>Albright, 2003, p. 207.</ref>。

1996年12月5日克林頓提名歐布萊特为国务卿候选人，在[[美国参议院|美国参议院]]一致通过后，于1997年1月23日宣誓就职，接替離任的[[沃倫·克里斯托弗|沃倫·克里斯托弗]]。

奥尔布赖特是美国史上第一位女国务卿<ref>{{cite web
 |url         = http://secretary.state.gov/www/albright/albright.html
 |title       = Biography: Madeleine Korbel Albright
 |publisher   = Office of the US Secretary of State
 |date        = 
 |accessdate  = 2010-07-09
 |deadurl     = yes
 |archiveurl  = https://web.archive.org/web/20160204185811/http://secretary.state.gov/www/albright/albright.html
 |archivedate = 2016-02-04
}}</ref>。任內主力解決[[波斯尼亞戰爭|波斯尼亞內戰]]以及中東和平方案。 奥尔布赖特曾经与[[柯林·鲍威尔|柯林·鲍威尔]]争论美军是否出兵波黑时说：“你们总是要保持美国的超级军事能力，但如果不去运用这种能力，又有什么意义？”<ref>"What's the point of you saving this superb military for, Colin, if we can't use it?" by Albright, 2003, p. 182.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://dissidentvoice.org/2010/10/the-evil-of-madeleine-albright/|title=The Evil of Madeleine Albright  -  Dissident Voice|website=dissidentvoice.org|access-date=2014-11-26|archive-date=2021-03-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210314153024/https://dissidentvoice.org/2010/10/the-evil-of-madeleine-albright/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2001年卸任，任[[乔治敦大学|乔治敦大学]][[埃德蒙·A·沃尔什外交服务学院|埃德蒙·A·沃尔什外交服务学院]]教授。

2022年3月23日，奥尔布赖特因癌症逝世于[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]，享年84岁<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.cnn.com/2022/03/23/politics/madeleine-albright-obituary/index.html|title=Madeleine Albright, first female US secretary of state, dies|first=Caroline|last=Kelly|date=2022-03-23|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2022-03-23|archive-date=2022-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220323183242/https://www.cnn.com/2022/03/23/politics/madeleine-albright-obituary/index.html|url-status=live}}</ref>。

